ARMOROFITHAN: Cast Armor of Ithan

Syntax: armorofithan
        armorofithan <target>

DESCRIPTION:
  Cast Armor of Ithan on yourself or a named target in the room.
  PPE cost: 10. Creates a 30 MDC magical field for about five minutes.

  Examples:
    armorofithan
    armorofithan ally
    cast armor of ithan

NOTES:
  Uses the standard cast path for spell-known, PPE, and combat checks.
  You must know the spell and have enough PPE.

SEE ALSO: cast, spells, armor_of_ithan
